&lt;p&gt;We currently have a part time Urology Support Clerk Post, to work with / support the Urology Nurse Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, energetic people person who will be at the forefront of our service, answering the phone and booking appointments and ensuring the service remains seamless for the patients attending our clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although this role is part time, there is an opportunity for this to develop into a full time role, should funding become available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jane Perkins  Lead Urology Nurse Practitioner  jane.perkins8@nhs.net  01438 284356&lt;/p&gt;
